Phoebe Noxolo Abraham (amụrụ na 7 Ọktoba, na afọ 1960) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa bụ onye otu National Assembly of South Africa
Ọ bụ onye otu African National Congress
Ọ bụ nọmba 103 nke ndepụta pati na ntuli aka South Africa nke afọ 2019.
Ọ bụ onye otu Standing Committee na Finance.
Ọ bụbu onye otu Eastern Cape Provincial Legislature.
